"this makes slimv autodetect the namespace of the buffer you are currently editing.
"Eval'ing forms will be evaled in their namespace without changing the REPL namespace.
let g:slimv_package = 1

"This will activate paredit mode!
"It's Vim's version of Emacs's paredit minor mode.
"Look at :help paredit to learn the keybindings. Highly recommended!
let g:paredit_mode = 1
